earing witness of Your Godhead, and I also save (the reward of) my loyalty to those with the recognition of whom You have bestowed upon me: namely, Muhammad and his Household, peace of Allah be upon them, (I save all that) to the day of my taking refuge with You, whether in this world or the Hereafter.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai ne Teri wahdaaniyat ka iqraar kiya, Teri zaat ko pehchaana, Tujh par khuloos ke saath imaan laaya, apna khaalis imaan aur Teri ruboobiyat Parwardigaari ka eteqaad rakkha, mai ne is wilaayat ko tasleem kiya jo Tu ne mujhe ataa ki, ba-wajah un ki shanaakht ke jo Teri makhlooq mein se hai Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki itrat (a.s), Khuda rehmat kare un par jis din Tere saamne khouf zadah hunge duniya o aakherat mein.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!میں نے تیری وحدانیت کا اقرار کیا تیری ذات کوپہچاناتجھ پرخلوص کے ساتھ ایمان لایااپنا خالص ایمان اورتیری ربوبیت و پروردگاری کا اعتقاد رکھا میں نے اس ولایت کو تسلیم کیا جو تونے مجھے عطا کی ان کی شناخت کے سبب سےجو تیری مخلوق میں سے ہیں محمدؐ اور ان کی عترت ؑ، خدا رحمت کرے ان پر جس دن تیرے سامنے خوف زدہ ہوں گا دنیا و آخرت میں۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE ZAKHARTO TAWHEEDEE IYYAAKA WA MA’REFATEE BEKA WA IKHLAASEE LAKA WA IQRAAREE BE-ROBOOBIYYATEKA WA ZAKAHRTO WELAAYATA MAN AN-A’MTA A’LAYYA BE-MA’REFATEHIM MIN BARIYYATEKA MOHAMMADIWN WA I’TRATEHI SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHIM LE-YAWME FAZA-E’E ILAIKA AAJELAN WA AJLAN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ ذَخَرْتُ تَوْحِیْدِیْ اِیَّاكَ وَمَعْرِفَتِیْ بِكَ وَاِخْلَاصِیْ لَكَ وَاِقْرَارِیْ بِرُبُوْبِیَّتِكَ وَذَخَرْتُ وِلَایَۃَ مَنْ اَنْعَمْتَ عَلَیَّ بِمَعْرِفَتِهِمْ مِنْ بَرِیَّتِكَ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّعِتْرَتِهٖ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْهِمْ لِیَوْمِ فَزَعِیْ اِلَیْكَ عَاجِلًا وَآجِلًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013522, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Thus, I am now taking refuge with You, O my Master, and with them, on this day and on this very situation, and I thus beg You for Your increasing bounties, for removing from me Your chastisement that I fear, for blessing all the sustenance which You grant me, and for immunizing my heart from receiving any grievous matter, any calamity, or any act of disobedience to You, regarding my religion, worldly life, and the Next Life. O most merciful of all those who show mercy.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Pas mai faryaad karta hu Tere aur un ke aaghe, ay mere Aaqa aaj ke din aur isi jagah jahan khada hu Tujh se sawaal karta hu keh mujhe apni neymat mein se hissa de aur Teri jis saza se darta hu woh mujh se dur kar de, jo rozi mujhe di us mein barkat de aur mere dil ko har andeshe se mehfooz rakh aur har na-gawaari aur na-farmaani se jo mere deen, meri duniya o aakherat mein ho, ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "پس میں فریاد کرتا ہوں تیرے اور ان کے آگے اے میرے آقا! آج کے دن اور اسی جگہ جہاں کھڑا ہوں تجھ سے سوال کرتا ہوں مجھے اپنی نعمت میں سے حصہ دے اور تیری جس سزا سے ڈرتا ہوں وہ مجھ سے دور کردے جو روزی مجھے دی اس میں برکت دے اور میرے دل کو ہر اندیشے سے محفوظ رکھ اور ہر ناگواری اور نافرمانی سے جو میرے دین میری دنیا اور آخرت میں ہو اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "WA QAD FA-ZE’TO ILAIKA WA ELAYHIM YAA MAWLAAYA FEE HAAZAL YAWME WA FEE MAWQEFEE HAAZAA WA SA-ALTOKA MAADDATEE MIN NE’MATEKA WA EZAAHATA MAA AKHSHAA-HO MIN NIQMATEKA WAL-BARAKATA FEEMAA RAZAQTANEEHE WA TAHSEENA SADREE MIN KULLE HAMMIWN WA JAAA-EHATIWN WA MA’SEYATIN FEE DEENEE WA DUNYAAYA WA AAKHERATEE YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "وَقَدْ فَزِعْتُ اِلَیْكَ وَاِلَیْهِمْ یَا مَوْلَایَ فِیْ هٰذَا الْیَوْمِ وَفِیْ مَوْقِفِیْ هٰذَا وَسَئَلْتُكَ مَادَّتِیْ مِنْ نِعْمَتِكَ وَاِزَاحَۃَ مَا اَخْشَاهُ مِنْ نِقْمَتِكَ وَالْبَرَكَۃَ فِیْمَا رَزَقْتَنِیْهِ وَتَحْصِیْنَ صَدْرِیْ مِنْ كُلِّ هَمٍّ وَّجَآئِحَۃٍ وَّمَعْصِیَۃٍ فِیْ دِیْنِیْ وَدُنْیَایَ وَاٰخِرَتِیْ یَآ اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBl